snippet.title: Saturn Longplay [031] Sonic 3D Blast
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: RickyC

This is my first time playing the Saturn version and there are a lot of nice graphical upgrades from the genesis. For this longplay I collect all chaos emeralds to get the good ending. -
